text: Enterprise is an unincorporated community in Catahoula Parish, Louisiana, United States. The community is located along the south bank of the Ouachita River and Louisiana Highway 124, north-northwest of Harrisonburg. Enterprise had a post office until it closed on October 15, 2011. It still has its own ZIP code, 71425 ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Catahoula Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana
title: Enterprise, Louisiana
